# screenshots

PuTTY captures, ping output, verification screenshots, photos of physical setup.

Naming: `<device>-phase<N>-<descriptor>.<ext>`
- `SW1-phase3-pingtest.png`
- `R1-phase3-show-ip-int-brief.txt`
- `setup-phase0-cable-routing.jpg`

Accepted formats: png, jpg, txt. Keep file sizes reasonable (<1 MB per image, resize/compress before commit).
